{"tid":2446064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墨西哥下院表決過關 娛樂用大麻合法近","createTime":"2021-03-14T06:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T07:16:32.000Z","uid":11506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"388cb290347254d9aaa71863d8ce173a83f4b132","tid":2446064,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T06:59:55.000Z","msg":"（中央社墨西哥市10日綜合外電報導）墨西哥國會下議院今天表決通過娛樂用大麻合法，讓這塊毒梟掌控的土地朝著轉型為巨大受管制市場向前更邁進一步。<br />\n<br />\n法案主旨之一，是要遏阻每年奪走這個拉丁美洲國家數千條性命的毒品暴力，今天在下院以316票贊成129 票反對通過後，仍須上院過關才能成為法律。若獲上院通過，有1.26億人口的墨西哥就將成為繼烏拉圭與加拿大之後，少數合法化娛樂用大麻的國家。"},{"pid":"53d4c76d5e85a2baff9291b56a80f345f44766b7","tid":2446064,"uid":11506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:01:13.000Z","msg":"墨西哥如果順利正式合法化全球價格應該會冇咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n供應急升"},{"pid":"16013b5b6d0ed6238442ecefaf70e09b8877b989","tid":2446064,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:08:47.000Z","msg":"合法化咗，毒眅反而成為輸家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655cf62e520a399c2b14ba54b44fac40f9043850","tid":2446064,"uid":11506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16013b5b6d0ed6238442ecefaf70e09b8877b989","tid":2446064,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:08:47.000Z","msg":"合法化咗，毒眅反而成為輸家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:15:31.000Z","msg":"war on drugs=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0eec375b2b90d0e0fbcdd66c3090b35813fb204","tid":2446064,"uid":126226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16013b5b6d0ed6238442ecefaf70e09b8877b989","tid":2446064,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:08:47.000Z","msg":"合法化咗，毒眅反而成為輸家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:16:32.000Z","ms